{"tid":2438761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉禾院線7間戲院放盤 傳大陸金主于品海染指香港影業","createTime":"2021-03-08T17:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T17:23:08.000Z","uid":37554,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e687f7bd189abf13e7cd17e9d0a308fd268758b","tid":2438761,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210308/SJGCDMRQOZH25PBYKLYF4DSMAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210308%2FSJGCDMRQOZH25PBYKLYF4DSMAQ%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rvw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=075dfa57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210308%2FSJGCDMRQOZH25PBYKLYF4DSMAQ%2F&h=f532e10a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210308/SJGCDMRQOZH25PBYKLYF4DSMAQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實嘉禾橙天於2017年已經將大陸院線76間電影院以36.8億港元出售給于品海旗下的南海控股，以加強于品海旗下大地院線在全國實力。在香港已擁有《香港01》新聞網媒的于品海，聽說對嘉禾橙天的香港院線也感興趣，雙方目前正在洽談。<br />\n<br />\n今日《蘋果》向橙天嘉禾求證是否院線正在放售中？橙天嘉禾發言人表示：「暫時冇回應。」如果大地院線真的買下嘉禾橙天香港院線，顯示于品海開始要染指香港戲院業務，增加在香港電影影壇的影響力。"},{"pid":"f151f1fa664ac9f783f243e02628613849605349","tid":2438761,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"01維穩院線？"},{"pid":"b7c66703920722b6323e5aa9e0cda5b3e7778b89","tid":2438761,"uid":9347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"又嚟，攪ATV仲未夠皮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35baa1ad1ace687445809398ed5f5456c7cd8982","tid":2438761,"uid":51041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭玩撚死香港d企業<br />\n就係諗住比d大陸佬賤價接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead